" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>Unir la educación básica y el trabajo mediante apr...</a></div><div class=\"post-relacionado relacionado9\" style=\"display: none;\"><a href=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/edu-news/oyes-o-escuchas/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"¿Oyes o escuchas?\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/franco-antonio-giovanella-PVDWaEhSIAg-unsplash-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"Oreja sobresale de cartón blanco.\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>¿Oyes o escuchas?</a></div><div class=\"flecha despues\"><a href=\"javascript:despuesRelacionado(1);\">&gt;</a><br><br><br><br></div></div>\n\t        \n        <div class=\"tags\">\n                    </div>\n        <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <a class=\"author-link\" href=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/edu-news/author/lemonscale/\" rel=\"author\">\n                <div class=\"avatar\">\n                    <img src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/plugins/wp-user-profile-avatar/assets/images/wp-user-thumbnail.png\">                </div>\n                <div class=\"author\">\n                    <strong>Observatorio IFE</strong> \n                </div>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"share-box\">\n                            <span>Compartir</span>\n                        <button id=\"fbShareBtn\" class=\"share-button\">\n  <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"shareOnFacebook('https%3A%2F%2Fobservatorio.tec.mx%2Fedu-reads%2Fradar-de-innovacion-educativa-2017%2F')\">\n    <img class=\"observatorio-logo\" src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/themes/observatorio-tec/assets/img/icons/facebook.png\" alt=\"facebook\">\n  </a>\n</button>\n\n<script>\n  function shareOnFacebook(url) {\n    window.open('https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=' + url, 'Facebook Share', 'width=600,height=400');\n  }\n</script>\n\n\n\n            <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/share?text=Radar de Innovación Educativa 2017&amp;url=\" id=\"twShareBtn\" class=\"share-button\"><img class=\"observatorio-logo\" src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/themes/observatorio-tec/assets/img/icons/twitter.png')\" alt=\"twitter\"></a>\n            <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https://observatorio.tec.mx/edu-reads/radar-de-innovacion-educativa-2017/\" id=\"liShareBtn\" class=\"share-button\"><img class=\"observatorio-logo\" src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/themes/observatorio-tec/assets/img/icons/linkedin.png')\" alt=\"linkedin\"></a>\n        </div>\n        \n        <p class=\"notecc\">Este artículo del <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.es \">Observatorio del Instituto para el Futuro de la Educación</a> puede ser compartido bajo los términos de la licencia CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 <img class=\"imgcc\" src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cc.png\"></p>\t",
